title: She Demons (1958) 76 min.DVDRip_Irish McCalla_Jonzee
description:
She Demons:  

Heroic, but dull, Fred Maklin and beautiful, but spoiled, Jerrie Turner wash 
up on an uncharted tropical island. They are soon captured by ex-Nazi Colonel 
Osler, who also has imprisoned a bevy of beauty contest winners whom he allows 
to be whipped by his slavering Nazi storm troopers. He has, you see, been 
extracting some glandular substance from the girls to inject into his wife Mona, 
who suffered terrible facial disfigurement, in efforts to restore her beauty. 
Things get worse as the island is used for test bombing by the US Air Force.

Stars: Irish McCalla, Tod Griffin, Victor Sen Yung, Rudolph Anders
